    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a showroom model. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining a factory-fresh luster without a single chip or scratch, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the premium upholstery. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle in peak condition with zero compromises.",
